message: No, this is not a listing of events. Adding events may violate [[WP:NPOV]] and [[WP:SYNTH]]: which events have "a right" to be added, and why the readers must be swayed by the particular view of one person on how an events affects (if anything) opinion polling? Most Wikipedia articles on opinion polling don't use events, and those that due are because some people add them unilaterally (like has been done here)
